name: Analysis Purpose
definition: Purpose of a specific analysis result described in ADaM analysis results metadata.

name: Analysis Reason
definition: Reason for reporting a specific analysis result described in ADaM analysis results metadata.

name: Date Imputation Flag
definition: Date Imputation Flag: Indicates the level of imputation reflected in a date value.
term: CDISC ADaM Date Imputation Flag Terminology

name: Derivation Type
definition: Derivation Type: Analysis value derivation method.

name: Geriatric Depression Scale Short Form Questionnaire Parameter Code
synonym: Geriatric Depression Scale Short Form Questionnaire Parameter Code
definition: A parameter code codelist for the Geriatric Depression Scale Short Form questionnaire (GDS02) to support the calculation of total score in ADaM.
term: CDISC ADaM Geriatric Depression Scale Short Form Questionnaire Parameter Code Terminology

name: Geriatric Depression Scale Short Form Questionnaire Parameter Name
synonym: Geriatric Depression Scale Short Form Questionnaire Parameter Name
definition: A parameter name codelist for the Geriatric Depression Scale Short Form questionnaire (GDS02) to support the calculation of total score in ADaM.
term: CDISC ADaM Geriatric Depression Scale Short Form Questionnaire Parameter Name Terminology

name: Parameter Type
definition: Parameter Type: Indicates whether the parameter is derived as a function of one or more other parameters.

name: Subject Trial Status
definition: Indicates the status of the subject in the trial.
term: CDISC ADaM Subject Trial Status Terminology

name: Time Imputation Flag
definition: Time Imputation Flag: Indicates the level of imputation reflected in a time value.
term: CDISC ADaM Time Imputation Flag Terminology
